# eBay Sales Finder
A Python project that uses the eBay Browse API to search listings and retrieve pricing data.
This project focuses on learning API integration, OAuth authentication, and backend structure
for future analysis and visualization.

# Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/ebay-sales-finder.git
cd ebay-sales-finder
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

Create a .env file in the project root:
CLIENT_ID=your_ebay_client_id
CLIENT_SECRET=your_ebay_client_secret
EBAY_ENV=sandbox

Run:
python src/backend/main.py

Notes:
.env is ignored; .env.example documents required variables
Uses the eBay Sandbox environment
Frontend and Flask integration are works in progress

Thatâ€™s it.

